Introduction to Matter.js is useful tutorial (uses p5.js to render)
https://github.com/liabru/matter-js/wiki/Tutorials


Running the system via a local server ...
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/16333790/node-js-quick-file-server-static-files-over-http


with node.js installed (and npm) ...

npm install http-server -g

go to folder ...

http-server -c-1   (-c-1 ensures to cache)

navigate to localhost:8080 or whatever port is requested.
